Texts.Chs:
如果你要搬到乡下，你会吃很多桃子。桃子被包装在这个罐子里。它们是由人放在那里的。很可能是来自市中心的某家工厂里。忍者不包括在内。
^green;类型：素食^reset;
Texts.Eng:
If you're moving to the country, you're gonna eat a lot of peaches. Peaches come in this can. They were put there by a man. Probably in some factory downtown. Ninjas not included.
^green;Type: Herbivore^reset;
